<view class="c13-drawer-page c13-step-four">
  <view class="c13-bg-report">
    <view class="c13-status"><text>9:41</text><text>wifi</text></view>
    <view class="c13-bg-top">
      <button bindtap="onReturnReport">‹</button>
      <text>完整报告</text>
      <text>错题 1 / 8</text>
    </view>
    <text class="c13-bg-title">AI 提分报告（完整）</text>
    <text class="c13-bg-time">报告生成时间：2024-05-30 10:36</text>
    <image class="c13-bg-owl c13-pointer-owl" src="/assets/icons/owl-teacher-pointer-transparent.png" mode="aspectFit" />
    <view class="c13-bg-score full">
      <view class="c13-score-row">
        <image class="c13-score-icon" src="/assets/icons/lock-purple.png" mode="aspectFit" />
        <view>
          <text>可追回分数</text>
          <text class="c13-score-sub">可优先改善</text>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="c13-score-value"><text>6-10</text><text>分</text><text>↗</text></view>
      <text class="c13-score-note">通过优先修复关键错因，有机会追回的分数区间</text>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class="c13-overlay light"></view>

  <view class="c13-drawer">
    <view class="c13-handle"></view>
    <view class="c13-drawer-head">
      <text>修复这道关键错题</text>
      <button bindtap="onReturnReport">×</button>
    </view>
    <view class="c13-progress">
      <view class="c13-line active-four"></view>
      <view class="c13-step done"><text>1</text><text>错因诊断</text></view>
      <view class="c13-step done"><text>2</text><text>换法讲解</text></view>
      <view class="c13-step done"><text>3</text><text>验证练习</text></view>
      <view class="c13-step active"><text>4</text><text>掌握判断</text></view>
    </view>
    <scroll-view class="c13-drawer-scroll" scroll-y="true" enhanced="true" show-scrollbar="false">
      <view class="c13-success">
        <text class="c13-check">✓</text>
        <text class="c13-success-title">初步掌握</text>
        <text>你已经理解了“速度差 × 时间 = 路程差”这个方法。</text>
      </view>
      <view class="c13-panel">
        <text class="c13-panel-title">掌握状态说明</text>
        <view class="c13-status-row good"><text>初步掌握</text><text>能在引导下正确应用方法</text></view>
        <view class="c13-status-row warn"><text>仍需复习</text><text>方法理解不稳定，需再练习</text></view>
        <view class="c13-status-row bad"><text>需要补前置知识</text><text>缺少必要知识，需先补齐</text></view>
      </view>
      <view class="c13-panel">
        <text class="c13-panel-title">已回写报告</text>
        <text class="c13-bullet">本题验证通过，已更新掌握状态：初步掌握。</text>
        <text class="c13-bullet">相关内容将在完整报告中同步更新。</text>
      </view>
      <view class="c13-actions">
        <button class="c13-secondary" bindtap="onReturnReport">返回报告</button>
        <button class="c13-primary" bindtap="onReturnReport">继续修复下一题</button>
      </view>
    </scroll-view>
  </view>
</view>
